Package: aisstream
Title: Live Vessel-Tracking Stream Client for AISStream.io
Version: 0.0.0.9000
URL: https://dereckscompany.github.io/aisstream,
    https://github.com/dereckscompany/aisstream
BugReports: https://github.com/dereckscompany/aisstream/issues
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Dereck",
           family = "Mezquita",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "dereck@mezquita.io",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9307-6762"))
Description: A thin R client for the AISStream.io live vessel-tracking WebSocket feed, built on connectcore. Open one socket, subscribe with bounding boxes plus optional MMSI / message-type filters, and handle raw frames Node-ws style. Reconnect, re-subscribe, keepalive and a watchdog are inherited; parse helpers and an NDJSON recorder included.
